# Environment variables — never commit these files
# Note: a .env file containing only publishable Supabase anon keys was committed
# in early history (commits f7673c6, 3794eea). Those keys are intentionally public
# (client-side) and cannot be rotated without breaking deployed clients, but the
# file is now excluded to prevent accidental exposure of future private keys.
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.staging

